  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat",
    "add the cumin, coriander, red chili flakes, and paprika and stir for 1 minute",
    "add the semolina and stir to coat with the spice mixture",
    "add the water, lemon juice, salt, and black pepper and stir to combine",
    "bring the mixture to a boil then reduce the heat to low and simmer for 20 minutes",
    "stir in the garlic and continue simmering for another 5 minutes",
    "transfer the mechoui to a serving platter and let it cool for a few minutes",
    "serve the mechoui warm or at room temperature",
    "you can also let it cool completely and refrigerate or freeze it for later use"
